No one wants an audience as they enjoy their outdoor space after a long week! Create beautiful spaces while adding essential privacy to your property with our sleek and sturdy Privacy Screens available in 8 unique patterns and 2 finishes.

Our Story Part 4: The Midland Planter began garnering the interest of Garden Centers like fresh buds popping up in early Spring. Surprisingly, they all had the same frustrations with existing “outdoor” products that failed to perform outdoors, of all places!

Fast forward to today, the original seed, which started as the Midland Planter and later transformed into Veradek Outdoor, is still growing! In addition to our all weather planters, we now offer a wide range of outdoor products from fire pits, outdoor kitchens, to privacy screens

A perfect pick for the passionate, motivated, and confident Aries is of course the impressive, and jaw dropping Bird of Paradise. All one can do is stare at what some would say is the main character of house plants. Its name is as spectacular as its features—reaching a potential height of 8 feet, and showcasing a remarkable display of rich foliage this plant baby is bound to impress. 

If you treat it right you may get to witness a spectacular leaf unfurling, or maybe even a bloom if you're lucky. Like an Aries the Bird of Paradise won't thrive long term out of the spotlight so make sure it has at least 4hrs of sun exposure each day to give it that golden hour glow. Top it off by giving it a stylish, reliable, and spacious new home with our Corten Pedestal Planter and tray.  Happy planting! 🌱
Create beautiful walls of greenery with our sleek and durable Metallic Span planter, available in 3 beautiful colors.
